Package: ColorPhage
Title: High-Aesthetic Palettes for Scientific Figures
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person(given = "xiaolw95", family = "ColorPhage", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "xiaolw95@163.com")
Author: xiaolw95 ColorPhage
Maintainer: xiaolw95 ColorPhage <xiaolw95@163.com>
Description: Provides high-aesthetic, publication-oriented colour palettes
    for scientific figures. Includes discrete palette families, ggplot2
    scale helpers for colour and fill, a matching publication theme, and
    first-pass continuous and diverging palettes for quantitative displays.
